  "detailed_description": "This game has an original story as base. This story will take place in a planet called \"EggPlanet\" in which chickens have different life styles, and you will advance on story as one of them.<br><br>The story will take place in a laboratory of certain government which investigate as egg which is about to explode.<br><br>Also you a chicken and the player, will have to complete simple tests(puzzles)  as chicken called noisy says.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Game Features are</h2>・<strong>You can be a chicken! so cute and colorful</strong><br>・Easy Puzzle And Hidden Story<br>・Completely original story<br>・30+ Test levels<br>・Mysterious and fantastic chicken world<br>・Simple Controll<br>・Beautiful 3D graphics<br>・Original Arts<br>・A chicken which can be customized",
